name: THE HERO WITH A THOUSAND FACES
description:
It is difficult to find a profession that this person would not have excelled in. He has excelled in the military, police, fireman, detective, teacher, engineer, businessman, karate master, trainer, pizza deliveryman and many others. For whatever business he undertook, he always did it excellently! An unsung hero of our time! Johnny Sins!
